@node "Document_5" "Registration"
@next "Document_6"
@prev "Document_4"
@{b}Registration@{ub}

BämsBackdropBrowser is Backdropware. If you
like it and use it, please register! To
register, send an e-mail to studio_bams@geocities.com
and attach your favourite backdrop. In the e-mail
you should include your e-mailaddress, your name,
and wether or not you want the studio BÄMS monthly
(well, almost) newsletter.
@endnode

