@node "Document_9" "The Future"
@next "Document_10"
@prev "Document_8"
@{b}The Future@{ub}

Future features of BämsBackdropBrowser:

o Text.  You'll be able to place text on the
         BBdB screen, so you can see if the
         backdrop will look nice with text on it.

o Icons. You'll be able to place icons on the
         BBdB screen, so you can see if the
         backdrop will look nice as Workbench Backdrop.

o Arexx support? If anyone wants this, then please
                 mail us: studio_bams@geocities.com,
                 and we'll include it..

o Anything else? Please send your ideas to
studio_bams@geocities.com

There will, however, NOT be a next version if noone
registers, or at least tells us what's wrong with the
program, so that we may correct it.
@endnode

